      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Jungle Guidebook",
        "Client": "Young Editor",
        "Description": "For the sake of my publication,\r\nI need you to hunt three monsters.\r\nI wish to record the nitty-gritty\r\ndetails of these fearsome beasts!\r\nOnce complete, merchants and\r\ntravelers will be able to navigate\r\nthe Jungle safely!",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Guide de la Jungle",
        "Client": "Jeune r\u00E9dacteur",
        "Description": "Il faudrait que tu chasses\r\ntrois monstres pour ma\r\npublication. Je veux noter un\r\nmaximum d\u0027informations sur\r\nces b\u00EAtes ! Comme \u00E7a, tout les\r\nmarchands pourront traverser\r\nla Jungle sans risque.",
        "Target": "Chasser tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Guida sulla giungla",
        "Client": "Giovane redattore",
        "Description": "Devi cacciare tre specie per\r\nla mia pubblicazione. Voglio\r\nriportare tutti i dettagli su\r\nquesti mostri in modo che\r\nviaggiatori e mercanti possano\r\nattraversare la giungla senza\r\nproblemi.",
        "Target": "Caccia tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Der Dschungelf\u00FChrer",
        "Client": "Junger Redakteur",
        "Description": "F\u00FCr mein Buch musst du drei\r\nMonster f\u00FCr mich erjagen.\r\nIch will das Wesen dieser Bestien\r\nauf Papier festhalten!. Dann\r\nk\u00F6nnen H\u00E4ndler und Reisende\r\nden Dschungel fortan sicher\r\ndurchqueren.",
        "Target": "Erjage alle Zielmonster.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "El libro de Jungla",
        "Client": "Joven editor",
        "Description": "Quiero que caces tres especies\r\npara mi publicaci\u00F3n. \u00A1Necesito\r\nplasmar todos los detalles de\r\nestos monstruos en papel!\r\nAs\u00ED, viajeros y mercaderes podr\u00E1n\r\ncruzar la Jungla sin peligro.",
